These are Puzzles for 4x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x6-Level-2-1::.
6 different pets are kept: goat, fish, pony, lizard, cat, hamster
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, blend, vegafina, old-henry, bongani, bluemaster
There are 6 different favourite colors: blue, fuchsia, coral, black, yellow, grey
House: victorian, tower, gothic-revival, craftsman, modern, futuristic
 1. the person who likes grey is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 2. the owner of the pony is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 3. the modern house is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 4. the person who likes yellow is between the person who likes fuchsia and the vegafina-smoker##2
 5. the owner of the goat is on the left of the victorian house##1
 6. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 7. the person who likes coral is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 8. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far left##1
 9. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
10. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
11. the craftsman house is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
12. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
13. the tower house is on the far left##1
14. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
15. the futuristic house is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
16. the gothic-revival house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |     5     |   6    |
| Pet          | hamster   | goat     | fish | lizard     | pony     | cat   |
| Cigar   | old-henry | bongani  | vegafina  | bluemaster | blend | fonseca |
| Color         | fuchsia | yellow | coral | black    | blue  | grey |
| House     | tower     | craftsman    | victorian    | modern   | futuristic      | gothic-revival    |

