There are 6 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, lemonade, soy-milk, tea, water
6 different pets are kept: frog, hamster, bird, horse, goldfish, rabbit
 1. the owner of the goldfish is the owner of the goldfish##1
 2. the person drinking tea is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
 4. the person who likes fuchsia is the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 6. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is the owner of the goldfish##1
 8. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1
 9. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
10. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
11. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
13. the person who likes fuchsia is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the frog##2
14. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who likes azure and the person driving the motorbike##2
15. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
16. the person driving the bus is the person who likes azure##1
17. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
